Package: ampliconstopremover
Title: Filter ASVs/OTUs Containing Stop Codons From FASTA File
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Ellen", "Smith", , "r03es23@abdn.ac.uk", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-9909-3451"))
Description: The package provides a single function to check for the presence of stop codons in amplicon sequences. It creates two output files: one with reads that did not contain stop codons, and one with those that did.
